---

<Layout title='About' description='Learn more about my journey into web development and the technologies I work with.'>
  <div class='container space-y-6'>
    <Breadcrumb />

    <article class='space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed'>
      <header class='space-y-6'>
        <h1 class='text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight lg:text-5xl'>About</h1>
        <div class='space-y-4'>
          <p>
            My journey into web development started with curiosity about how websites worked, which quickly evolved into
            a passion for <span class='highlight'>building innovative digital experiences</span>.
          </p>

          <p>
            With a <span class='highlight'>degree in Computer Science</span>, I've focused on mastering modern web
            development and creating solutions that make a difference. From browser extensions to full-stack
            applications, I approach each project as an opportunity to innovate and grow.
          </p>

          <p>
            Today, I specialize in building <span class='highlight'>modern web applications</span> that prioritize performance,
            accessibility, and user experience. I'm particularly passionate about exploring new technologies and finding creative
            ways to solve complex problems through code.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class='space-y-6' aria-labelledby='tech-stack'>
        <h2 id='tech-stack' class='text-2xl font-bold'>Tech I Love Working With</h2>
        <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-6' role='list' aria-label='Technology stack'>
          {
            techStack.map((tech) => (
              <a
                href={tech.url}
                target='_blank'
                rel='noopener noreferrer'
                role='listitem'
                class={cn(
                  'bg-base-200 hover:bg-base-300 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 rounded-lg p-4 transition-all duration-300',
                  'hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]',
                  tech.hover,
                )}
              >
                <Icon name={tech.icon} class={cn('size-8 opacity-85', tech.color)} aria-hidden='true' />
                <span class='text-base-content text-sm font-medium'>{tech.name}</span>
              </a>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class='space-y-6' aria-labelledby='fun-facts'>
        <h2 id='fun-facts' class='text-2xl font-bold'>Fun Facts</h2>
        <div class='grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2' role='list' aria-label='Personal fun facts'>
          {
            funFacts.map((fact) => (
              <div
                role='listitem'
                class={cn(
                  'bg-base-200 group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-lg p-4',
                  'hover:bg-base-300/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5',
                  'transition-all duration-300 ease-out',
                  'hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]',
                  fact.hover,
                )}
              >
                <div class='relative'>
                  <Icon
                    name={fact.icon}
                    class={cn('size-5 shrink-0', 'transition-all duration-300', fact.color, 'group-hover:scale-110')}
                    aria-hidden='true'
                  />
                  <div
                    class={cn(
                      'absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-0 blur-sm',
                      'transition-opacity duration-300 ease-out',
                      'group-hover:opacity-50',
                      fact.color.replace('group-hover:', ''),
                    )}
                    aria-hidden='true'
                  />
                </div>
                <span>{fact.text}</span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <aside class='from-secondary/20 to-warning/20 space-y-4 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r p-6 text-lg'>
        <p>
          I'm always open to discussing new projects, opportunities, or just having a chat about web development. Feel
          free to check out my <a href='/projects' class='text-secondary hover:text-secondary/80 font-medium underline'
            >projects</a
          > or head over to the <a href='/contact' class='text-secondary hover:text-secondary/80 font-medium underline'>
            contact page</a
          > to get in touch.
        </p>
        <nav class='flex items-center gap-2' aria-label='Contact links'>
          <Button href='mailto:hello@aleksa.codes' variant='outline' size='sm'>
            <Icon name='lucide:mail' aria-hidden='true' />
            <span>Email</span>
          </Button>
          <Button href='/contact' variant='outline' size='sm'>
            <Icon name='lucide:message-square' aria-hidden='true' />
            <span>Contact</span>
          </Button>
        </nav>
        <p class='font-cursive text-right text-3xl font-bold select-none sm:text-4xl' aria-hidden='true'>aleksa</p>
      </aside>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
